解：逐項檢查：選項 \(\sqrt{6} \div (\sqrt{2} + \sqrt{3})\)，分母有理化得 \( rac{\sqrt{6} \cdot (\sqrt{3} - \sqrt{2})}{(\sqrt{3} + \sqrt{2})(\sqrt{3} - \sqrt{2})} =  rac{\sqrt{18} - \sqrt{12}}{3 - 2} = 3\sqrt{2} - 2\sqrt{3}
eq \sqrt{3} + \sqrt{2}\)，故此項錯誤；選項 \((\sqrt{7} - \sqrt{3})^2 = 7 - 2\sqrt{21} + 3 = 10 - 2\sqrt{21} 
eq 4\)，故此項錯誤；選項 \((\sqrt{6} - \sqrt{3})(\sqrt{6} + \sqrt{3}) = 6 - 3 = 3\)，正確；選項 \((\sqrt{7} + \sqrt{3}) \cdot \sqrt{10} = \sqrt{70} + \sqrt{30} 
eq 10\)，故此項錯誤。選項 \((\sqrt{6} - \sqrt{3})(\sqrt{6} + \sqrt{3}) = (\sqrt{6})^2 - (\sqrt{3})^2 = 6 - 3 = 3\) 正確，故選：\((\sqrt{6} - \sqrt{3})(\sqrt{6} + \sqrt{3}) = (\sqrt{6})^2 - (\sqrt{3})^2 = 6 - 3 = 3\)。本題考查二次根式的運算與平方差公式。
